#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:6
msgid "Blender is available for download for Linux, macOS and MS-Windows."
msgstr "Blender提供Windows, Linux以及 Mac平台下的程序下载。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:10
msgid "Minimum Requirements"
msgstr "最低配置要求"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:12
msgid ""
"Check if your system meets the `minimum or recommended requirements <https://www."
"blender.org/download/requirements/>`__."
msgstr ""
"请查看你的系统是否符合 `最低或推荐配置要求 <http://www.blender.org/download/"
"requirements/>`__."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:15
msgid ""
"Always check that the graphics drivers are up to date and that OpenGL is well "
"supported."
msgstr "一定要将显卡驱动升级到最新版，确认OpenGL得到良好支持。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:17
msgid ""
"Support for other hardware such as graphic tablets and 3D mice are covered later "
"in :doc:`Supported Hardware </getting_started/installing/configuration/"
"hardware>`."
msgstr ""
"关于外设的支持，比如3D鼠标和绘图板的支持请看后面的 :doc:`支持硬件列表 </"
"getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware>`."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:22
msgid "Download Blender"
msgstr "下载 Blender"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:24
msgid ""
"The Blender Foundation distributes Blender in three different ways that you can "
"choose from, to better suit your needs."
msgstr "Blender基金会通过三个途径发布Blender程序，你只需要选择你觉得合适的就行。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:27
msgid ""
"The options comprise binary packages for all the supported platforms and the "
"source code. Within the binary packages, you can choose from a stable release or "
"a daily build. The first has the benefit of being more reliable, the latter "
"provides the newest features, as they are developed. Blender is released "
"approximately every three months. You can keep up to date with the latest "
"changes through the `release notes <https://www.blender.org/features/releases/"
">`__."
msgstr ""
"这些选择项涵盖了所有受支持平台的二进制安装包和源代码。如果是用二进制包安装，你可"
"以选择一个稳定发布版或者每日编译版。前者的好处是更加可靠，后者则可以提供最新的仍"
"在开发的功能特性。Blender大约每3个月发布一次版本。你可以通过 `发布说明 <https://"
"www.blender.org/features/releases/>`__ 来了解最新的变化。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:34
msgid "`Latest Stable Release <https://www.blender.org/download/>`__"
msgstr "`最新稳定版 <http://www.blender.org/download/>`__"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:34
msgid ""
"This is a binary distribution of the latest version of Blender. It is considered "
"stable and without regressions."
msgstr "这是Blender最新版的二进制发布版。非常稳定和有良好兼容的。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:38
msgid "`Daily Builds <https://builder.blender.org/download>`__"
msgstr "`每日编译版 <http://builder.blender.org/download>`__"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:37
msgid ""
"This is a binary distribution of Blender that is updated daily to include the "
"newest changes in development. These versions are not as thoroughly tested as "
"the stable release, and might break, although they are official and generally "
"not highly experimental."
msgstr ""
"这是每日更新的二进制发布版，包含了最新的开发变化。该版本与稳定版相比是未经历全面"
"测试，并可能崩溃的，尽管这也是官方版本，且通常并非高度试验性。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:45
msgid ""
"`Build from Source <https://wiki.blender.org/index.php/Dev:Doc/"
"Building_Blender>`__"
msgstr "`从源代码编译 <https://developer.blender.org/diffusion/B/>`__"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:41
msgid ""
"Blender's source is available for reference and installation, with the following "
"advantages:"
msgstr "Blender提供源代码供参考和安装，具备以下优势："

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:43
msgid "Blender is always up to date."
msgstr "Blender总是在更新的。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:44
msgid ""
"It allows access to any version or branch where a feature is being developed."
msgstr "允许获取任意版本或者正在开发的分支版。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:45
msgid "It can be freely customized."
msgstr "也可以自由地定制化。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:49
msgid ""
"This is included for completeness, but it is **not** expected that regular users "
"should have to compile their own Blender builds."
msgstr ""
"这里提到源码编译只是为了手册的全面性，**并不** 奢求常规用户自己去编译Blender程"
"序。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/introduction.rst:54
msgid "Install Blender"
msgstr "安装Blender"

